'''班傑明·A·「班」·佛斯特'''（{{lang-en|Benjamin A. "Ben" Foster}}，{{bd|1980年|10月29日||}}）是一名美國男演員。曾獲得艾美獎和美國演員工會獎。他在電影《[[飛揚的年代|飛揚的年代]]》（1999年）和《[[失戀大不同|失戀大不同]]》（2001年）中為人所熟悉，其他著名電影包括《[[終極人質|終極人質]]》（2005年）、《[[布魯斯威利之終極黑幫|布魯斯威利之終極黑幫]]》（2006年）、《[[變種特攻：兩極爭霸|變種特攻：兩極爭霸]]》（2006年）和《[[屍城30夜|屍城30夜]]》（2007年）。

2007年，他因西部片《[[決戰3:10|決戰3:10]]》中的演出而獲得[[土星獎|土星獎]]和[[衛星獎|衛星獎]]的提名<ref name="oohav">{{cite web |title=Ben Foster |work=Yahoo! Movies |year=2010 |url=http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800332837/bio |accessdate=2010-11-15 |archive-date=2011-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628221851/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800332837/bio |dead-url=no }}</ref>。後來又參與了《[[極速秒殺|極速秒殺]]》（2011年）、《[[禁運品|禁運品]]》（2012年）和《[[紅翼行動_(電影)|紅翼行動]]》（2013年）。2016年，佛斯特於電子遊戲改編電影《[[魔獸：崛起|魔獸：崛起]]》中飾演麥迪文。

==早期生活==
班·佛斯特出生於波士頓，父親史提芬·佛斯特和母親吉琳安·科萬是麻薩諸塞州一間餐廳的老闆<ref name="dlanot">{{Cite news |last=Fee |first=Gayle |author2=Laura Raposa |title=Inside Track: Pool barons foster son's fledgling career |work=Boston Herald |date=1995-09-03 |url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/bostonherald/access/20531991.html?dids=20531991:20531991&FMT=ABS |accessdate=2010-11-15 |archive-date=2013-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130319113940/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/bostonherald/access/20531991.html?dids=20531991:20531991&FMT=ABS |dead-url=no }}{{subscription}}</ref><ref name="notsob">{{Cite news | last = Sherman | first = Paul | title = New ''Heights''; After landing the lead role in Barry Levinson's latest film, Boston native Ben Foster is flying | work = Boston Herald | date = 1999-12-09 | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/bostonherald/access/47037101.html?dids=47037101:47037101&FMT=ABS | accessdate = 2010-11-15 | archive-date = 2013-03-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130319113930/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/bostonherald/access/47037101.html?dids=47037101:47037101&FMT=ABS | dead-url = no }}{{subscription}}</ref><ref name="rekr">{{Cite news |last=Abel |first=Judy |title=Exploring life’s ‘darker corners’ |work=The Boston Globe |date=2009-11-15 |url=http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/articles/2009/11/15/ben_foster_addresses_grief_and_loss_in_the_messenger/?page=2 |accessdate=2010-11-15 |archive-date=2009-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091118145105/http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/articles/2009/11/15/ben_foster_addresses_grief_and_loss_in_the_messenger/?page=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他有一個弟弟[[喬恩·福斯特|喬恩]]也是位演員。當福斯特四歲的時候，他的家人遷往愛荷華州的[[費爾菲爾德_(愛荷華州)|費爾菲爾德]]，在此之前他們的波士頓舊居所曾被劫匪闖入<ref name=rekr/><ref name="Foster1">{{cite web |last=Miller |first=Gerri |title=Foster Reaches for the "Heights" |work=JVibe |year=1999 |url=http://www.jvibe.com/popculture/heights.shtml |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20000523011623/http://www.jvibe.com/popculture/heights.shtml |archivedate=2000-05-23 |accessdate=2006-11-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

佛斯特是[[猶太教|猶太人]]，並完成了成年禮的儀式<ref name="Foster1"/><ref name="nol">{{Cite news |last=Sragow |first=Michael |title=It's a boy's, boy's, boy's world (and a girl's) |work=Salon.com |date=1999-12-16 |url=http://www.salon.com/entertainment/col/srag/1999/12/16/liberty_heights |accessdate=2010-11-15 }}{{dead link|date=十月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。他的祖父母是西莉亞（西格爾）和亞伯拉罕·福斯特，分別是一名著名法官和波士頓政客；他們的家庭來自於[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]的移民<ref name="Associated">{{cite news |last=Breed |first=Allan G. |title=Ben Foster reaches for new ''Heights'' |work=Lawrence Journal-World |date=1999-02-04 |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=6oEyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=veYFAAAAIBAJ&pg=5145,1266634&dq=ben-foster-reaches-for-new-heights&hl=en |accessdate=2007-12-10 |archive-date=2018-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180919164433/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=6oEyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=veYFAAAAIBAJ&pg=5145,1266634&dq=ben-foster-reaches-for-new-heights&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/boston/doc/290724968.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Dec%2027,%201994&author=Indira%20A.R.%20Lakshmanan,%20Globe%20Staff&pub=Boston%20Globe%20(pre-1997%20Fulltext)&edition=&startpage=&desc=A.%20Frank%20Foster,%20judge%20who%20once%20halted%20a%20man's%20beating;%20at%2084 | work=Boston Globe | first=Indira A.R. | last=Lakshmanan | title=A. Frank Foster, judge who once halted a man's beating; at 84 | date=1994-12-27 | accessdate=2015-09-04 | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304035713/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/boston/doc/290724968.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Dec%2027,%201994&author=Indira%20A.R.%20Lakshmanan,%20Globe%20Staff&pub=Boston%20Globe%20(pre-1997%20Fulltext)&edition=&startpage=&desc=A.%20Frank%20Foster,%20judge%20who%20once%20halted%20a%20man's%20beating;%20at%2084 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://brezniakrodman.com/obituary/celia-segal-foster/ |title=CELIA ( SEGAL) FOSTER « Brezniak Rodman Funeral Directors |publisher=Brezniakrodman.com |date=2010-06-28 |accessdate=2014-05-12 |archive-date=2013-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203001723/http://brezniakrodman.com/obituary/celia-segal-foster/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。佛斯特會進行靜坐冥想的活動<ref name=hae>{{Cite news |last=DeYoung |first=Bill |title=Extreme closeup: Ben Foster |publisher=Connect Savannah |date=2009-10-27 |url=http://www.connectsavannah.com/news/article/101305/ |accessdate=2010-11-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101108041903/http://www.connectsavannah.com/news/article/101305/ |archivedate=2010-11-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在費爾菲爾德生活時他就讀了[[瑪赫西管理大學|瑪赫西管理大學]]。

==個人生活==
於2012年初開始，他和女演員[[羅蘋·萊特|羅蘋·萊特]]開始交往<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20569270,00.html|title=Robin Wright and Ben Foster Get Cozy|date=2012-02-10|publisher=People.com|accessdate=2013-04-19|archive-date=2016-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423063227/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20569270,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/robin-wright-46-and-ben-foster-32-affectionate-during-shopping-trip-20122412 | title = Robin Wright, 46, and Ben Foster, 32, Affectionate During Shopping Trip | date = 2012-12-24 | author = Justin Ravitz | publisher = US Magazine | accessdate = 2013-04-19 | archive-date = 2020-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200818102702/https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/robin-wright-46-and-ben-foster-32-affectionate-during-shopping-trip-20122412/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他們在2014年初決定結婚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20774776,00.html|title=Robin Wright and Ben Foster are engaged|date=2014-01-11|author=Alexis L. Loinaz|publisher=People.com|accessdate=2014-01-11|archive-date=2016-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531102148/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20774776,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但於2014年11月12日取消了訂婚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/robin-wright-ben-foster-split-call-off-engagement-details-20141211|title=Robin Wright and Ben Foster Split, Call Off 10-Month Engagement -- Find Out What Went Wrong|date=2014-11-12|first=Sierra|last=Marquina|work=Us Magazine|accessdate=2014-11-13|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225084923/https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/robin-wright-ben-foster-split-call-off-engagement-details-20141211/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來又復合<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/03/robin-wright-april-2015-cover|title=Introducing Robin Wright, Our April 2015 Cover Star|publisher=Vanity Fair|accessdate=2015-09-04|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302174823/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/03/robin-wright-april-2015-cover|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年8月29日，他們正式宣布結束了這段關係<ref>{{cite web|last1=Webber|first1=Stephanie|title=Robin Wright, Ben Foster Call Off Engagement For the Second Time|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/robin-wright-ben-foster-call-off-engagement-for-the-second-time--2015298|accessdate=2015-08-29|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118134911/https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/robin-wright-ben-foster-call-off-engagement-for-the-second-time--2015298/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年10月，福斯特和女演員[[蘿拉·普萊潘|蘿拉·普萊潘]]訂婚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://people.com/style/laura-prepon-ben-foster-engagement-ring/|title=Laura Prepon and Ben Foster Are Engaged! See Her Gorgeous New Ring|date=2016-10-05|publisher=people|access-date=2018-06-04|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125144339/https://people.com/style/laura-prepon-ben-foster-engagement-ring/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 2017年1月，兩人正在等待他們的第一個孩子<ref>{{cite web|url=http://people.com/babies/laura-prepon-pregnant-baby-bump-sundance-film-festival/|title=Pregnant Laura Prepon Steps Out with Baby Bump at Sundance Film Festival|date=2017-01-24|publisher=people|access-date=2018-06-04|archive-date=2018-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180705033035/https://people.com/babies/laura-prepon-pregnant-baby-bump-sundance-film-festival/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。普萊潘在2017年8月生下他們的女兒Ella。2018年6月，福斯特和普萊潘結婚<ref>{{cite web|url=https://people.com/movies/laura-prepon-ben-foster-are-married/|title=Laura Prepon and Ben Foster Are Married! 'Thank You for All the Love'|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|date=2018-06-03|accessdate=2018-06-04|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129192921/https://people.com/movies/laura-prepon-ben-foster-are-married/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

